<p>2.右击App，我们使用里面的样式数据来进行演示</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210524095034172.png" alt="image-20210524095034172" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>3.直接打开即可</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210524095046693.png" alt="image-20210524095046693" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>4.使用此数据来做图</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210524095127627.png" alt="image-20210524095127627" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h6 id="font-color008b8b作图font"><font color='#008B8B'>作图</font></h6>
<p>1.选中数据，使用折线图</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210524095233085.png" alt="image-20210524095233085" loading="lazy"></figure>
